        <updateDate>2003-09-30T20:29:58Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Homestead Preservation Act - Directs the Secretary of Labor to establish a program of low-interest loan (residential) mortgage assistance to eligible persons who are separated from their employment.</p> <p>Limits assistance to 12 months, and requires repayment within five years.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
